name: Crob_Vel
content: Crob Vel was a Gamorrean male criminal who dealt in illicit merchandise. Vel hired the bounty hunter Boba Fett, who owed him a debt, to delay the smugglers Han Solo and Chewbacca in bringing him a delivery so that he could then force Solo to continue working for him to make up for it. Fett's intervention was successful, and the bounty hunter declared to Vel that his debt had been paid off.
